data.description: Discover this Charming Historic Family Home, ideally located near the Hospital, Library, Schools, and Shopping. This 4/5 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath home exudes charm. The main floor offers a spacious living area with refinished hardwood floors, a modern kitchen with cooktop, detached oven, and ceramic floors, plus a versatile second dining/office space opening to a deck. The walk out basement is finished with a full bath with a jet tub, that can adapt to your needs, whether a 5th bedroom, in-law suite, a family/theater/entertainment/bar area, or rent it out for passive income. This charming home also comes with a concrete driveway leading to a 2-car detached garage. This historic home perfectly blends classic style with modern comfort! Don't miss out on this unique opportunity, it's a Must See!
